# rz_negpi4 — Rz(-π/4) = e^{i(π/8)Z}. Pauli-Z 지수 회전(해밀토니안 시뮬 primitive). analytic golden.
```python id=bloq
import numpy as np
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import Rz
bloq = Rz(-np.pi/4)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
golden = np.diag([np.exp(1j*np.pi/8), np.exp(-1j*np.pi/8)]).astype(complex)
```
